windows-64-bit-heres-the-key-thing = Ecce le cosa clave a saper: applicationes 64-bit pote usar plus memoria e tende a collaber minus que applicationes 32-bit. In ultra, post le transition de 32 a 64 bits, un function de securitate que se appella <a href="{ $ASLR }">Address Space Layout Randomization</a> (ASLR; rearrangiamento aleatori del spatio de adresses) functiona melio qua protection contra attaccantes. Quanto al usatores de { -brand-name-linux } e { -brand-name-mac }, sia tranquille: vos jam usa un version 64-bit de { -brand-name-firefox }.
